# OMEGA Project Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` first. It is the single source of truth for all agent rules.

## Key Principles

- ECONOPHYSICS > SWE — physics supersedes standard engineering
- δ = 0.5 is a universal constant (Sato 2025)
- Constitution: `OMEGA_CONSTITUTION.md`
- Project manual: `handover/README.md`
- Live state: `handover/ai-direct/LATEST.md`

## Commands

- Tests: `python3 -m pytest tests/ -q`
- Deploy: `python3 tools/deploy.py`
- Health: `python3 tools/cluster_health.py`
- Env: `python3 tools/env_verify.py --strict`

## Banned

- No SCP for code deployment
- No hardcoded paths — use `configs/node_paths.py`
- No secrets in git
- No Float32 for physics math
